{
  "version": 1,
  "course": {
    "id": "nce1-111-112-the-most-expensive-model",
    "title": "Lesson 111: The most expensive model",
    "audioFilename": "111&112－The Most Expensive Model.mp3",
    "duration": 115.069,
    "language": "en"
  },
  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "start": 0.62,
      "end": 2.6,
      "text": "Lesson 111.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "第111课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "start": 4.06,
      "end": 6.42,
      "text": "The Most Expensive Model.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "最昂贵的型号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "start": 8.24,
      "end": 12.08,
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "start": 13.78,
      "end": 14.6,
      "text": "Can Mr.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "弗里斯先生"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "start": 14.94,
      "end": 18.2,
      "text": "Frith buy the television on installments?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "能分期付款购买这台电视机吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "start": 19.66,
      "end": 21.08,
      "text": "How does it work?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它怎么操作？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "start": 23.56,
      "end": 26.42,
      "text": "I like this television very much.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我非常喜欢这台电视机。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "start": 27.28,
      "end": 28.94,
      "text": "How much does it cost?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "它多少钱？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "start": 29.94,
      "end": 33.9,
      "text": "It's the most expensive model in the shop.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这是店里最昂贵的型号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "start": 34.62,
      "end": 36.7,
      "text": "It costs £500.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "售价500英镑。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "start": 38.32,
      "end": 41.56,
      "text": "That's too expensive for us.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这对我们来说太贵了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "start": 42.28,
      "end": 45.12,
      "text": "We can't afford all that money.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们付不起那么多钱。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "start": 45.88,
      "end": 49.3,
      "text": "This model's less expensive than that one.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "这个型号比那个便宜。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "start": 50.06,
      "end": 58.26,
      "text": "It's only £300, but, of course, it's not as good as the expensive one.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "只要300英镑，不过当然没有那台贵的好。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "start": 59.7,
      "end": 61.98,
      "text": "I don't like this model.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我不喜欢这个型号。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "start": 62.8,
      "end": 67.98,
      "text": "The other model's more expensive, but it's worth the money.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "另一个型号更贵，但物有所值。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "start": 69.42,
      "end": 72.04,
      "text": "Can we buy it on installments?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我们能分期付款买吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "start": 72.98,
      "end": 73.84,
      "text": "Of course.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "当然可以。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "start": 74.58,
      "end": 83.16,
      "text": "You can pay a deposit of £30 and then £14 a month for three years.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "您可以先付30英镑定金，然后连续三年每月付14英镑。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "start": 84.4,
      "end": 86.04,
      "text": "Do you like it, dear?",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "亲爱的，你喜欢吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "start": 87.22,
      "end": 92.02,
      "text": "I certainly do, but I don't like the price.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "我当然喜欢，但我不喜欢它的价格。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "start": 92.98,
      "end": 98.1,
      "text": "You always want the best, but we can't afford it.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "你总想要最好的，可我们买不起。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "start": 98.76,
      "end": 103.04,
      "text": "Sometimes you think you're a millionaire.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "有时你觉得自己是个百万富翁。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "start": 105.36,
      "end": 108.78,
      "text": "Millionaires don't buy things on installments.",
      "translations": {
        "zh-Hans": "百万富翁可不会分期付款买东西。"
      }
    }
  ]
}
